CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet - Baby Chapter - The baby chapter of Girl Friends scintillate on the Detroit scene. Here are Johnnie Fritz, Mary Agnes Davis, Essel Saulsberry and Allene McCampbell"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four members of Detroit's Girl Friends, Inc., including Johnnie Fritz, Mary Agnes Davis, Essel Saulsberry, and Allene McCampbellt, standing in interior with dot patterned carpeting, floral curtains, and piano for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
